descr: "The Measure resource provides the definition of a quality measure."

fields.name: identifier
fields.descr: "A unique identifier for the group. This identifier will used to report data for the group in the measure report."

fields.name: name
fields.descr: "Optional name or short description of this group."

fields.name: description
fields.descr: "The human readable description of this population group."

fields.name: stratifier
fields.descr: "The stratifier criteria for the measure report, specified as either the name of a valid CQL expression defined within a referenced library, or a valid FHIR Resource Path."
